{"tid":1981260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【偽 · 正視聽】得啦我知我洗咗你地版，召喚聯署師長文Q&A就放喺度啦","createTime":"2020-04-20T14:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-28T16:40:25.000Z","uid":320074,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"31caa2b9d36fe279d9527951f33aca5ddcaac600","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:26:20.000Z","msg":"各位手足先say句sor先，<span style=\"font-size: small;\">因為小弟突然之間睇到某個po講李柱銘</span>，好心急想send個睇法出嚟。但你知㗎啦，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">小弟受眾又唔多，又係個分化撚【係啊我係反對進攻功能組別 + 好戰巴啊，但我唔甘心咁樣就自廢武功，今日篇幅所限。】</span>。所以無人推好正常既【仲要膠】。<br />\n不過，今日點講都好，重點如下啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">召喚聯署師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzYVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=9b0368de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a></span></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\">裡面有好多為香港打定安全網既聯署<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n假如我地唔打好 我地好難用<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">最低程度既損傷</span><br />\n去真正<span style=\"color: orange;\">光復香港 奪權當家<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></div><br />\n前一兩日李柱銘俾狗塔，但喺美國政壇引起如此大既迴響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。正係<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為先前聯署同請求美帝落實《人權及民主法案》而致</span>，趁機<span style=\"color: teal;\">俾藉口美帝加速打殘狗共</span>，何樂不為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n1.你話，小，我光復香港既目標都唔同~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答：但你咁樣係可以<span style=\"color: teal;\">幫到國際戰線+其他戰線既手足wo，兄弟爬山可以共同努力㗎，你幫我，我幫你咁解姐</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.你又話，小，會曬我時間㗎，我時間好寶貴㗎~<br />\n答：去vote4 hk 簽署到confirm signature<span style=\"color: gold;\">【記得一定要出Your signature has been confirmed個畫面你先簽到聯署㗎】，唔夠1分鐘，<span style=\"color: teal;\">幾個聯署咪最多曬你十分鐘左右</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n黃色Youtuber圈都話要CLS【其實應該再多個 No Skip既，因為咁樣可以令果個Youtuber收到錢錢，咪做到更加多高質既片俾你地咯~】<br />\n</span><br />\n聯署都可以嚟個<span style=\"color: teal;\">SECS</span>㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">S: Sign【簽署聯署】<br />\nE: Email【去Email度Click封聯署確認信】<br />\nC: Confirm【確認有綠色提示字】<br />\nS: Share【俾更多人一齊簽，眾志成城】<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">3.你又話，小，我一個簽又無人簽，玩撚啊？</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答: 恭喜你答到問題所在啦~ 你一個簽係唔夠㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，所以要<span style=\"color: gold;\">些牙</span>，同<span style=\"color: gold;\">玩個聯署challenge，邊個簽咗一個聯署就Tag三個人，而果三個人亦要接受挑戰，自己簽完一個聯署再tag三個人</span>，如此類推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<span style=\"color: orange;\">616都做到200萬人</span>，<span style=\"color: gold;\">69都做到100萬人啦</span>，聯署要<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">10萬</span></span>咋wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，成10倍既容錯率，點計我地都著數啦~<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">香港人最鍾意跣人蕉皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你咪可以喺幫到運動既同時合法地跣一鑊，對方又唔會話你撚化佢既，搞掂~</span><br />\n<br />\n4.你又話，小，我憎鳩外國勢力㗎【同時適合於政治潔癖】<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n答：其實呢，就同你<span style=\"color: gold;\">憎鳩飯民</span>既道理一樣【我都係憎鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】，你憎鳩咪<span style=\"color: teal;\">利用佢最大功用</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: teal;\">用完咪當佢condom咯</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<span style=\"color: red;\">飯民點解可以隨時當你condom</span>，咪就<span style=\"color: teal;\">因為佢喺需要既位度利用到你既最大功用</span>，用完咁咪搞掂當condom咯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。同樣地，你憎鳩外國勢力，就要利用外國勢力對你既最大公倍數嚟達成你既目標。大家既目標都係要<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，實現雙普選㗎</span>，再經<span style=\"color: teal;\">民選政府</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">實現五大訴求</span>㗎係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話就唔多講啦，<span style=\"color: gold;\">連結就喺上面~記得些牙，簽曬佢啊</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">國族自主自強，構築香港共同體<br />\n重新立約，還我民主<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路<br />\n</span></span><br />\nP.S. 約 = 社會契約論，有興趣自己google~"},{"pid":"32328feabf51b86d65c8e401d88564ee4cbcf287","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"推啊 唔好拉啊 我分化撚姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但先國家之急而後私讐啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc774bfff22aa43f022d6bb9a288f539378f71c","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"分化撚既一個請求 我唔想呢個都被鬥啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2750483504756ee9bc2fd1e66c5fb16ec499a53","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"求推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a6a9cb6363b54bc34d0c4ed507e23dbb093edfc","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:05:40.000Z","msg":"同樣報道相關既高質PO【純粹私心揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />】<br />\n排名不分先後~<br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: gold;\">外媒政要關注港共高調拉人 李柱銘：自己被捕感覺「舒服曬」 終於有機會同優秀既香港年青人同行民主路</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1977864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1977864</a><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: orange;\">拉一個李柱銘可以trigger到八國聯軍咁發聲</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1979203\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1979203</a><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: teal;\">討論區入嚟多謝曱甴強鳩拉李柱銘導致全球再次關注香港</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1979217\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1979217</a><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Twitter十級大火！美國英國聯合國歐盟澳洲加拿大意大利台灣國際高度關注李柱銘被捕！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1979007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1979007</a><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: pink;\">查理斯王子：我們任由香港聽天由命，但願民主黨的李柱銘不會被捕</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978284\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978284</a><br />\n<br />\n- <span style=\"color: violet;\">討論區李柱銘發起新式鬥黃  唔鬥人地鬥自己</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978064</a>"},{"pid":"ead44571940f4fc3dbe742e7ab3379b0faaf9aa2","tid":1981260,"uid":248358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:16:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"618daaf347d95fa12914c026132f3d1563b77849","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"推啊 聯署同國際戰線好撚緊要啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d788c2043688587d479519a5f4cdb0095f50342e","tid":1981260,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:27:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1829fe75fbc6717321308b12fdb634413d31f73","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"幾個聯署要大家簽同緊急推啊 仲差一日咋<br />\nDeadline之前簽咗佢同些牙，命運自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.香港獨立【差52000 = 約20倍係100萬，約40倍就係200萬】<br />\n<br />\n2.調查資產轉移，凍結資產【差94000 = 約156倍係100萬，約310倍就係200萬】"},{"pid":"390f3aef79feb0b2befda22555cb431687ebade0","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1829fe75fbc6717321308b12fdb634413d31f73","tid":1981260,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:28:15.000Z","msg":"幾個聯署要大家簽同緊急推啊 仲差一日咋<br />\nDeadline之前簽咗佢同些牙，命運自主<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.香港獨立【差52000 = 約20倍係100萬，約40倍就係200萬】<br />\n<br />\n2.調查資產轉移，凍結資產【差94000 = 約156倍係100萬，約310倍就係200萬】"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T15:31:07.000Z","msg":"shi唔記得Highlight<br />\n<br />\n1.香港獨立【差52000 = 約<span style=\"color: maroon;\">20倍</span>係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">100萬</span>，約<span style=\"color: maroon;\">40倍</span>係<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">200萬</span>】<br />\n<br />\n2.調查資產轉移，凍結資產【差<span style=\"color: red;\">9400